For this extension to work, you need to open it when your current tab is in Instagram's domain (like instagram.com). You also must be logged in.

This extension allows you to view and export (to CSV) lists of users you follow or who follow you on Instagram. There's also a special list called "Not Mutual" that shows users you follow but don't follow you back. Another interesting feature is the "Ignored" list, where you can specify a username to be ignored from "Not Mutual" list. 

These features are useful for you to manage who you follow, who follows you and find out who don't follow you back.
